[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3011] some dependencies
, fixed the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3049] Rust 1.50 clippy warnings
andrasio prevented 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3012] selecting the same column twice
, improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3016] coercions for column-path
Qwanve fixed 
``ps``
 output 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3015] when the process doesn't have a parent
ilius extended 
``which``
 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3024] to allow for multiple applications to be passed
