``sort-by``
, did some 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3033] formatting and clean-up of nu-parser
, switched to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3035] metric/standard filesizes
, added a way 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3045] to switch to metric filesizes
, improved the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3048] serialization conversion for column-path
