Path: Nushell base
Content:
jonathandturner updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3011] some dependencies
, fixed the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3049] Rust 1.50 clippy warnings
andrasio prevented 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3012] selecting the same column twice
, improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3016] coercions for column-path
Qwanve fixed 
``ps``
 output 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3015] when the process doesn't have a parent
ilius extended 
``which``
 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3024] to allow for multiple applications to be passed
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3025] reverse to 
``sort-by``
, did some 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3033] formatting and clean-up of nu-parser
, switched to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3035] metric/standard filesizes
, added a way 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3045] to switch to metric filesizes
, improved the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3048] serialization conversion for column-path
fdncred added a new 
